====================
Gaim iFolder Plugin
====================
The iFolder Project website can be found at:
http://forge.novell.com/modules/xfmod/project/?ifolder

The Gaim iFolder Plugin allows you to share iFolders with people in your Gaim
Buddy List.  The Gaim iFolder Plugin is free software, licensed under the
GNU GENERAL PUBLIC LICENSE (see the COPYING file).

Copyright (C) 2004 Novell, Inc.

---------------------------------
Building the Gaim iFolder Plugin
---------------------------------

First, you must build Gaim.  Follow the instructions available from
http://gaim.sourceforge.net/ for your particular platform and come back to
these instructions.

Copy "ifolder.c" to the "gaim/plugins" directory (or create a symbolic link that
points to "ifolder.c" in this directory.  From the "gaim/plugins" directory
type the following to build the plugin:

Linux
------

	make ifolder.so

Win32
------

	make -f Makefile.mingw ifolder.dll

-----------------------------------
Installing the Gaim iFolder Plugin
-----------------------------------

Once you've got a library (.so/.dll), copy (or create a symbolic link) the
library file to the following directory:

	<your gaim prefix>/lib/gaim/

Now start Gaim and the iFolder Plugin will be available from the "Preferences"
window under "Plugins".


---------------------
Discussion & Support
---------------------

    A mailing list for Simias and iFolder discussion is available.

    You can subscribe to the mailing list by visiting:

        http://forge.novell.com/mailman/listinfo/ifolder-dev


